query:
SELECT
                        al.id,
                        al.account_id,
                        al.action,
                        al.details,
                        al.created_at,
                        a.email AS "account_email?",
                        a.name AS "account_name?"
                    FROM audit_log al
                    LEFT JOIN account a ON al.account_id = a.id
                    WHERE al.organization_id = $1
                    ORDER BY al.created_at DESC, al.id DESC
                    LIMIT $2
